---
---
<div class="space-y-14">
  <div>
    <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 uppercase mb-3">Services</p>
    <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] lg:text-[2rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-3 leading-tight">Two models, one goal: operational excellence</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.9375rem] max-w-2xl">Choose the engagement that fits your stage and risk preference.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
    <article class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mb-2">Managing Director as a Service</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed mb-5">Fractional executive leadership for your existing Romania operation or new site—to stabilize, scale, and remove delivery noise.</p>
      <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-500 uppercase mb-3">Included</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Executive rhythm: KPIs, meeting cadence, decision discipline</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Hiring and retention: recruitment funnel, onboarding, performance</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Budget and cost control: transparent reporting, vendor management</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Delivery stability: escalation paths, risk management, accountability</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> AI rollout in operations: safe adoption with human review</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" /></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mb-2">Build-Operate-Transfer (BOT)</h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed mb-5">We set up and scale your Romania site (Timisoara and West Romania) with a predictable delivery operating system. Transfer to you when ready.</p>
      <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.12em] text-zinc-500 uppercase mb-3">Included</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed mb-6">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Launch sprint: legal and vendor setup, onboarding, office or coworking</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Recruiting engine: role scorecards, sourcing, structured interviews</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Operating cadence: weekly steering, KPIs, action tracking</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Delivery governance: priorities, risks, escalation, stakeholder reporting</li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-zinc-300 mt-0.5 text-[0.75rem]">→</span> Transfer option: handover playbook and leadership transition</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 pt-5 border-t border-zinc-700/50 text-[0.8125rem] text-zinc-400">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span> Build (4–8 weeks)</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span> Operate (3–24 months)</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-400"></span> Transfer (optional)</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
